Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:49.35,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:53.29,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,except for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:03:00.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:03.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:06.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,turned to rubber after \Nhe ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.71,0:03:09.14,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his friends venture into that sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:16.60,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.62,0:03:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others formed a \Npirate alliance with Trafalgar Law{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and have come to Dressrosa\Ngoverned by the Warlord - Donquixote Doflamingo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.55,0:03:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They took down the executives of\Nthe Donquixote Family one after another.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.09,0:03:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And finally, Luffy brought down Doflamingo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.47,0:03:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.65,0:03:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The Strongest Creature!\NOne of the Four Emperors - Kaido, King of the Beasts!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His brother was just here but\Nhe's sleeping peacefully, totally unaware.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be disappointed when he wakes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.77,0:04:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a nice brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.52,0:04:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I can barely fix myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.20,0:04:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He really is a nice brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.08,0:04:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we wake you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.95,0:04:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, were you listening to Sabo's story?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, from about halfway through.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.75,0:04:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must've been speaking...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.07,0:04:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...quieter than our captain's snoring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.74,0:04:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we wake him up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.88,0:04:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, let him sleep as much as he likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought him here for just that reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.38,0:05:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoroland, maybe there is alcohol\Nin the cellar under the kitchen floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.14,0:05:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You think so?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much I thank Luffyland,\Nit could never be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.36,0:05:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way of knowing how much he \Nencouraged the people of Dressrosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This country will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.45,0:05:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to all of you, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pain from the wounds that\Nyou're all suffering from...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.50,0:05:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is the result of injuries you sustained\Non behalf of us, the citizens of Dressrosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.71,0:05:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to repay you somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.30,0:05:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna have a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you gonna sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Am I disturbing you?\N--No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.74,0:05:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna spar with you someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.59,0:06:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe a famous swordsman \Nsuch as you said that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.08,0:06:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.70,0:06:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe someday when our wounds heal...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.79,0:06:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it was mine to begin with...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.17,0:06:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take a rest, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.09,0:06:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me some meat...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.77,0:06:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.03,0:06:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soldier-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.57,0:06:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.20,0:06:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw the list in the Colosseum.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.79,0:06:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You entered the competition as I thought.\NI told you not to!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.54,0:06:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.96,0:06:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it! I'll win it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soldier-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:07:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... Hey, can we live together?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.88,0:07:37.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, the so-called Twirly Hat Crew\Nwho headed for Zou,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.55,0:07:45.55,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,a mysterious island in the New World, is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.02,0:07:54.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.40,0:07:59.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want you to take him and head for Zou!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:03.28,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Twirly Hat Crew took Caesar, \Nthe scientist from Punk Hazard
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:06.27,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,who ate the Gas-Gas Fruit, with them...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:10.27,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...as they set out to meet\NLuffy and the others at Zou.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.29,0:08:15.86,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But they were targeted by Big Mom, one \Nof the Four emperors, on their way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.88,0:08:19.95,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her desire was to capture Caesar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna get caught by Big Mom!\NBecause I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...swindled research funds from them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.16,0:08:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let anyone take \Nyou anyway so shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.15,0:08:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You go ahead and sail for Zou!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.84,0:09:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.05,0:09:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all the struggle\Nto shake up Big Mom's ship...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.39,0:09:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you wanna get into trouble again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no choice! Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.57,0:09:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.03,0:09:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no time for grumbling!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.74,0:09:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you kick me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.87,0:09:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying it for the sake of you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.33,0:09:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stick your nose in their business!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.06,0:09:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should've waited on the ship quietly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.67,0:09:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty stupid to be \Nrushing ahead like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.92,0:09:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and do what I say!\NAre you gonna do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you just want your \Nheart to be crushed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.54,0:09:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! But I won't forget this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.52,0:09:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the right call to come ashore!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:10:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can still save them! We need your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.66,0:10:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case,\Nwhy don't you treat me more nicely...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.22,0:10:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop taunting me with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,0:10:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.12,0:10:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said "Don't tell me \Nwhat to do"! You raccoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a reindeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.57,0:10:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the difference?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.61,0:10:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Just hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.26,0:10:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they die because of you,\NI'll make you pay for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.64,0:10:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to run here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe we got separated \Nfrom Sanji-{\i1}san{\i0} and the others...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.16,0:10:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We paid too much attention \Nto the mystery girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.71,0:11:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, watch out! Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Watch out! I gotta save myself!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.05,0:11:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, how could you?!\NHow could you?! How could you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.06,0:11:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Brook.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.35,0:11:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onami! They're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.73,0:11:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeehaw!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.32,0:11:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.38,0:11:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this it, invaders?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.64,0:11:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Where did you hide that girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.95,0:11:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you guys invade the island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.55,0:12:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me! This place is quite atypical...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.31,0:12:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.94,0:12:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.15,0:12:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Rain-Ruption!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.33,0:12:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.14,0:12:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.79,0:12:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What {\i1}is{\i0} that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.79,0:12:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rain?! No! It's a huge water spray!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming, it's coming, it's coming,\N it's coming! It's coming this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No!\N--No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.72,0:12:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.77,0:12:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.11,0:12:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.99,0:12:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momonosuke-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.87,0:13:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.93,0:13:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy! You Devil Fruit eaters \Nare such pains in the butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.47,0:13:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry that I couldn't protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.93,0:13:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you get away! You damn invaders!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.36,0:13:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Brace up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.32,0:13:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you as always...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.41,0:13:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, too, Momo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.31,0:13:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.46,0:13:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When in doubt...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:14:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.74,0:14:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When in doubt...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.91,0:14:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.92,0:14:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Brook!\N--Bonekichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.88,0:14:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally managed to protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.84,0:14:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the rest up to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk! How arrogant!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.10,0:14:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheep's Horn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.52,0:14:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.17,0:14:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What are those arms?!\N--Bonekichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.36,0:14:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.92,0:15:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Parade!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Bonekichi, that's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of ability is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.92,0:15:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Keep stalling him like that!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.59,0:15:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diable! Mouton...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Mallet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.69,0:15:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheepshead-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.11,0:15:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.24,0:15:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.02,0:15:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are {\i1}you{\i0} people... Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.87,0:15:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! How creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.33,0:15:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-Rummy-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Retreat!\NSheepshead-{\i1}sama{\i0} has been taken down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.67,0:15:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:16:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we haven't found the samurai yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although we cornered them this far,\Nhe didn't show himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The samurai's not here! Tell him so!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.92,0:16:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.03,0:16:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The water's draining away...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a strange island.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.83,0:16:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope that girl's okay, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She moves quicker than \Nus so she'll be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.48,0:16:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.85,0:16:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.91,0:16:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get over here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.77,0:16:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Chopperemon!\NFrom the forest down below!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:17:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go now! There's no time to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.49,0:17:12.49,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,THE KID PIRATES' SAFE HOUSE
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.38,0:17:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.51,0:17:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! There's a massive hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.27,0:17:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--A hole?\N--Something landed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Arm yourselves!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.02,0:17:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.63,0:17:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is big.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:17:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did it fall from?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.44,0:18:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who in the world did this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.13,0:18:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, doesn't it look like \Nthe shape of a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I once heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.68,0:18:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a legend about a Sky Island\Nwhere some monster lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,0:18:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...somewhere in the sky around here.\NHave you ever heard that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.44,0:18:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that\Nit was pushed off of a Sky Island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of our ships was capsized by the impact!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.91,0:18:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it all! Who did this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.62,0:18:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The strong live and the weak die.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That is just how this world is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A few minutes ago...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:57.60,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,A SKY ISLAND - THE RUINED \NCITY OF BALLOON TERMINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.29,0:19:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave him alone, Monk!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.30,0:19:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.09,0:19:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're at a height of 10,000 meters...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He was looking for a place to die.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.34,0:19:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's serious, why bother to stop him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.43,0:19:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To sum up his life,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.93,0:19:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he had been defeated seven times as a pirate{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.93,0:19:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and was captured\Nby the Navy or his enemies 18 times.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.23,0:19:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He underwent torture repeatedly\Nand had been living as a criminal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.12,0:19:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He wanted to kill himself...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.47,0:20:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...by jumping off a Sky Island\Nwhich is rather out of the ordinary...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.80,0:20:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's what led up to this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.43,0:20:15.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It bears repeating.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.46,0:20:18.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,He challenged the Navy and the \NFour Emperors single-handedly{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.59,0:20:23.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and was captured 18 times;\Nsentenced to death 40 times.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.65,0:20:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When he was hanged, the chain broke.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.41,0:20:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When he was sent to a guillotine,\Nthe blade shattered.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.02,0:20:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When sentenced to impalement,\Nthe spear crumbled.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.68,0:20:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Consequently, he sank \Nnine giant prison ships.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That means no one could kill him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even himself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.79,0:21:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.08,0:21:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that monster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.38,0:21:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! My head hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.71,0:21:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's hard to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.67,0:21:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I survived again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.01,0:21:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He managed to pull off dying...\NThat old man, Whitebeard...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.82,0:21:57.82,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The man looking for a place to die -\NKaido, King of the Beasts.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:09.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"If it's one-on-one, Kaido will win."\NThat's what people say.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.05,0:22:14.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On land, sea, and air, he \Nis a pirate who is known
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.54,0:22:22.54,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,as the strongest creature \Namong all living things.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.81,0:22:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice now, do I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.58,0:22:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.00,0:22:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, Joker!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.29,0:22:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make preparations for the final battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.54,0:22:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if this boring \Nworld is destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.84,0:23:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start the greatest war \Nthe world has ever seen!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.78,0:23:13.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dressrosa celebrates King Rikufs \Nrestoration to the throne
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.35,0:23:16.59,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,after a decade and the debut \Nof their new princess, Rebecca.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.61,0:23:19.54,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, when the Navyfs heavyweights, \N"Inspector General" Sengoku
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.56,0:23:22.70,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and "Great Advisor" Tsuru, \Nshow up in front of Fujitora,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.72,0:23:25.79,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the die that will determine Luffy \Nand the others' fate is cast!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.81,0:23:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.48,0:23:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fujitora Takes Action! The \NComplete Siege of the Straw Hats!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.92,0:23:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
